text: Samuel Alexander Moran (born 4 April 1978) is an Australian entertainer. He is best known for having been a member of the children's band The Wiggles from 2006 to 2012. He was born in Sydney and raised in Wagga Wagga. He hosted the children's television series Play Along With Sam until April 2020. ==References== Category:1978 births Category:Living people Category:Australian pop singers Category:Australian pop musicians Category:Australian guitarists Category:Australian television presenters Category:Musicians from Sydney Category:Actors from Sydney
